Cypher: MATCH (n3:Gene) WHERE NOT ((:Anatomy{ name: "bulbo-urethral gland" })-[:EXPRESSES_AeG]->(n3)) RETURN n3.name UNION MATCH (n3:Gene) WHERE NOT ((:Compound{ name: "Bretylium" })-[:UPREGULATES_CuG]->(n3)) RETURN n3.name
